trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of all <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptReference"></xref> controls that are defined in a Web page's <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManager"></xref> control and <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"></xref> controls.

trans-unit.source: The collection that is returned includes framework scripts that are sent automatically to the client to support AJAX functionality such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> and <xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel> control.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen som returneres inneholder framework-skript som sendes automatisk til klienten som støtter AJAX funksjonaliteten som den <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>og <xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: When you use the GetScriptReferences method, be aware of the following guidelines: - Script references with the same <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Name%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Assembly%2A> properties are removed as duplicates.
trans-unit.target: Når du bruker metoden GetScriptReferences, være klar over følgende:-skriptet referanser med samme <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Name%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Assembly%2A>egenskapene har blitt fjernet som duplikater.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Assembly%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Script references with the same <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A> are not removed as duplicates at design time.
trans-unit.target: -Skriptet referanser med samme <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A>fjernes ikke som duplikater under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A>

trans-unit.source: However, they are removed as duplicates at run time.
trans-unit.target: Fjernes de som duplikater på kjøretidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ResolveClientUrl%2A> method is used to return a fully qualified URL for the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A> property of script references.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ResolveClientUrl%2A>Metoden brukes til å returnere en fullstendig URL-adresse for den <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A>for skriptet referanser.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ResolveClientUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The script references in the returned collection are cloned versions of the original script references and therefore cannot be modified in designer code by using this collection.
trans-unit.target: -Skript-referanser i samlingen returnerte er klonede versjoner av de opprinnelige skriptet refererer til, og derfor kan ikke endres i designer kode ved hjelp av denne samlingen.
